Cleaning with UNGER

UNGER - Professional cleaning supplies for professional glass and building cleaners

With more than 60 years of experience, UNGER ensures the best quality, efficiency and innovation in the field of cleaning products for professional glass and building cleaning. Through continuous development and innovative cleaning systems, UNGER focuses with its products on integrated solutions that make cleaning fast, effective and particularly user-friendly. In the field of building cleaning and professional glass cleaning, UNGER offers not only cleaning tools and systems, but also other accessories and cleaning tools ranging from dust removal to solar cleaning with pure water.

Your benefits

Innovation

By developing innovative cleaning systems, UNGER provides highly professional solutions for building cleaners and glass cleaners.

Efficiency

The highly ergonomic cleaning systems from UNGER support you in making your daily work even easier, more thorough and more efficient.

Quality

With UNGER cleaning products, professional building cleaners can rely on the best quality and safety in a wide range of applications.

Service

Our customer service always ensures a fast and smooth delivery and takes care of your concerns professionally.
